few_shot_examples.output:
Title: 销售额驱动因素深度分析
Mode: YvsX
Y-Dimensions: [销售额]
X-Dimensions: [客流量, 广告投入]
Smoother: MovingAverage

Data:
- { 销售额: 5000, 客流量: 100, 广告投入: 500 }
- { 销售额: 7000, 客流量: 150, 广告投入: 800 }
- { 销售额: 3000, 客流量: 80, 广告投入: 300 }

erDiagram
    USER ||--o{ ORDER : "下单"
    ORDER ||--|{ PRODUCT : "包含"

    USER {
        int user_id PK
        string name
    }
    ORDER {
        int order_id PK
        datetime create_time
    }
    PRODUCT {
        int product_id PK
        float price
    }

classDiagram
    class Vehicle {
        <<interface>>
        +move()
    }
    class Car {
        -engine: Engine
        +start()
        +stop()
    }
    class Engine {
        +cylinders: int
        +ignite()
    }

    Vehicle <|.. Car
    Car *-- Engine

Title: 智能终端市场趋势
ColorPalette: tech
Font[Title]: 24
Font[Base]: 14

Spec: {
  "type": "common",
  "series": [
    {
      "type": "bar",
      "data": { "values": [
        { "year": "2021", "value": 35, "type": "Smartphone" },
        { "year": "2022", "value": 42, "type": "Smartphone" },
        { "year": "2023", "value": 48, "type": "Smartphone" },
